EngDesc.value: This threat downloads the malicious lupper worm binary file that then is executed to infect new hosts. This threat file contains a very large server side response file, which takes a while to load. Please wait a few Minutes after loading the threat. This threat connects to a webserver to download the malicious binary, which typically listens on port 80. This threat is a client side attack and uses the virtual server. (IPv6 Version)
